/-- **The `(2,3)` B├йzout certificate** (PROVEN, sympy-extracted
Sylvester-adjugate cofactors): `F тмЭ ╬итВВSq + G тмЭ ╬итВГ = тИТ╬Ф┬▓` modulo the
`b`-invariant relation, so `╬итВВSq` and `╬итВГ` cannot vanish together
when `╬Ф тЙа 0`. -/
